# The files necessary to set up and run EPW calculation

## espresso-4.0.3
   - source directory for EPW-compatible version of espresso with EPW-2.3.6 inside its ./EPW folder

## makefiles
   - makefiles for a different systems

## executables
   - executables for different systems

## scripts
   - directory containing the wrappers for a complete many-step EPW calculation

## psp
   - directory containing the EPW-compatible pseudopotentials in UPF1 format
  
## tar
   - original files from http://www.quantum-espresso.org/previous-versions and http://epw.org.uk/Main/DownloadAndInstall